\(\omega=2 \pi f=2 \times 3.14 \times 50=314 \mathrm{rad} / \mathrm{sec}\)
\(I=\cfrac{V}{\sqrt{R^{2}+\omega^{2} L^{2}}} \Rightarrow 0.5=\cfrac{100}{\sqrt{100^{2}+(314 L)^{2}}}\)
\(\therefore L=0.55 \mathrm{H}\)
